            "id": 6411759,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 道瓊指數大漲2.89%，報47929.69點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間08日09:40，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>上漲1345.23點（或2.89%），暫報47929.69點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+0.52%</li><li>近 1 月：-1.93%</li><li>近 3 月：-4.92%</li><li>近 6 月：-0.04%</li><li>今年以來：-3.08%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>成分股以宣偉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SHW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SHW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SHW-US</a>)領漲。宣偉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SHW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SHW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SHW-US</a>)上漲7.11%；卡特彼勒(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CAT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CAT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CAT-US</a>)上漲6.14%；高盛集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GS-US</a>)上漲5.99%；家得寶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:HD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/HD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">HD-US</a>)上漲5.91%；美國運通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AXP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AXP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AXP-US</a>)上漲4.87%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，雪佛龍(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CVX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CVX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CVX-US</a>)下跌6.08%；威瑞森電信(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:VZ:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/VZ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">VZ-US</a>)下跌2.41%；嬌生(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:JNJ:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/JNJ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">JNJ-US</a>)下跌1.2%；可口可樂(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:KO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/KO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">KO-US</a>)下跌0.32%；默克藥廠(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRK:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRK\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRK-US</a>)下跌0.28%。</p></section></main>",
